  Bridge  The  not  stadium  a Q  The answer must be a situation when the victim is going to participate in a court case. The victim is going to take stand, which means they are going to testify. Runaway is not related to taking stand in a court case. Witness is a person who sees something, but the victim is the one who is going to testify. Tell truth is a common phrase used in court cases, but it is not what the victim is going to do. Go home is not related to taking stand in a court case. So the answer is testify (a).

